{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"42":{"eng-name":"Model Behavior of the Prophet (Kitab Al-Sunnah)","ara-name":"كتاب السنة"}},"section_detail":{"42":{"hadithnumber_first":4596,"hadithnumber_last":4772,"arabicnumber_first":4596,"arabicnumber_last":4772}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":4616,"arabicnumber":4616,"text":"حدثنا ابو كامل، حدثنا اسماعيل، حدثنا خالد الحذاء، قال قلت للحسن { ما انتم عليه بفاتنين * الا من هو صال الجحيم } قال الا من اوجب الله تعالى عليه انه يصلى الجحيم","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih Isnaad Maqtu"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih Isnaad Maqtu"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":42,"hadith":21},"chapter":{"id":7,"ara-name":"باب لُزُومِ السُّنَّةِ","eng-name":"Adherence To The Sunnah","isFirstHadith":false}}]}